18
00:00:12,540 --> 00:00:15,540
http://hiqve.com/

19
00:00:18,564 --> 00:00:19,941
<i>Villainy swells!</i>

20
00:00:20,066 --> 00:00:23,110
<i>With an army of the galaxy's
most vicious criminals,</i>

21
00:00:23,194 --> 00:00:25,279
<i>Darth Maul and Savage Opress</i>

22
00:00:25,363 --> 00:00:28,115
<i>conspire with Pre Vizsla
and the Death Watch</i>

23
00:00:28,199 --> 00:00:31,202
<i>to topple Duchess Satine,
ruler of Mandalore.</i>

24
00:00:31,786 --> 00:00:35,873
<i>While the conspirators prepare to attack
the Mandalorian capital of Sundari</i>

25
00:00:35,957 --> 00:00:37,458
<i>from a base on Zanbar,</i>

26
00:00:37,542 --> 00:00:41,295
<i>the fate of 2, 000 other neutral systems
is under threat,</i>

27
00:00:41,420 --> 00:00:45,716
<i>as Darth Maul moves closer
to establishing a vast criminal empire.</i>

28
00:00:46,968 --> 00:00:48,010
Where are my targets?

29
00:00:48,469 --> 00:00:50,805
We've identified them at these locations.

30
00:00:50,888 --> 00:00:52,890
However, as I've said before,

31
00:00:52,974 --> 00:00:58,020
if we try to take Mandalore by force,
our people will turn against us.

32
00:00:58,604 --> 00:01:02,817
I will use my army of crime lords

33
00:01:02,900 --> 00:01:07,071
to attack different targets across Sundari
and sow chaos

34
00:01:07,405 --> 00:01:09,490
to undermine the Duchess's rule.

35
00:01:10,199 --> 00:01:14,662
Our gangsters will make her look too weak
to maintain control.

36
00:01:15,162 --> 00:01:17,999
Then you and your Death Watch
will capture and arrest us,

37
00:01:18,040 --> 00:01:22,211
bringing order where
Satine's weak government could not.

38
00:01:22,670 --> 00:01:23,671
We'll be saviors.

39
00:01:24,589 --> 00:01:25,673
Exactly.

40
00:01:26,549 --> 00:01:27,592
A good plan.

41
00:01:27,925 --> 00:01:30,303
Indeed. I'll prepare the troops.

42
00:01:39,478 --> 00:01:41,856
It's a risk to trust those monsters.

43
00:01:42,189 --> 00:01:44,191
How do we know
they'll keep their end of the bargain?

44
00:01:44,525 --> 00:01:47,236
We need those Sith and their thugs
to cause some pain

45
00:01:47,361 --> 00:01:51,282
and show the Mandalorian people
how weak Satine really is.

46
00:01:51,365 --> 00:01:52,533
After this is done,

47
00:01:52,658 --> 00:01:55,036
no one will doubt why we're in power.

48
00:01:55,369 --> 00:01:56,871
Most will welcome us.

49
00:01:57,038 --> 00:01:58,122
Then what?

50
00:01:58,289 --> 00:02:00,958
Then we execute Maul and those thugs.

51
00:02:01,042 --> 00:02:04,045
Those criminals will scatter,
and Mandalore will be ours.

52
00:02:09,550 --> 00:02:12,053
I believe Vizsla will betray us.

53
00:02:12,887 --> 00:02:14,722
We have no other choice.

54
00:02:15,348 --> 00:02:19,060
We cannot rule openly
without drawing the attention of the Jedi.

55
00:02:19,477 --> 00:02:22,730
We need Vizsla as the face of our rule.

56
00:02:22,897 --> 00:02:23,898
For now.

57
00:02:24,565 --> 00:02:28,027
The promise of wealth
will find us a new face on Mandalore.

58
00:02:28,444 --> 00:02:30,863
You've learned well, my apprentice.

59
00:02:31,572 --> 00:02:34,950
Greed never fails to motivate.

60
00:03:00,935 --> 00:03:02,103
What's the matter?

61
00:03:02,436 --> 00:03:06,941
I am scanning life forms.
I believe this spice shipment is infested.

62
00:03:07,775 --> 00:03:09,110
Step back.

63
00:03:09,735 --> 00:03:10,778
Ah!

64
00:03:11,320 --> 00:03:13,447
Gangsters! We're under attack!

65
00:03:18,119 --> 00:03:21,956
Surrender!
My master is taking over these docks.

66
00:03:22,081 --> 00:03:25,793
You are now under the control
of the Pyke Syndicate.

67
00:03:28,629 --> 00:03:30,965
Duchess, the shipping docks
are under attack.

68
00:03:31,340 --> 00:03:33,134
By whom? The Death Watch?

69
00:03:33,509 --> 00:03:36,178
No, it appears to be a crime syndicate.

70
00:03:36,470 --> 00:03:38,639
Our guards are helpless
against their numbers.

71
00:03:38,848 --> 00:03:42,309
And the people are demanding
we do something to stop them.

72
00:03:45,646 --> 00:03:46,939
Welcome to Mandalore!

73
00:03:50,276 --> 00:03:51,318
Stand down!

74
00:03:51,652 --> 00:03:54,822
You're now all slaves of the Black Sun Clan.

75
00:03:57,992 --> 00:03:59,118
Fall back!

76
00:04:03,664 --> 00:04:05,499
It's the gangsters. Lock the vaults.

77
00:04:06,000 --> 00:04:07,501
Open the bank!

78
00:04:07,626 --> 00:04:09,670
We're here for a withdrawal.

79
00:04:10,004 --> 00:04:11,130
Guards, now!

80
00:04:16,010 --> 00:04:19,180
The Black Sun is attacking the vaults.
Send reinforcements.

81
00:04:28,647 --> 00:04:29,690
Take him.

82
00:04:35,488 --> 00:04:36,530
Ah!

83
00:04:43,913 --> 00:04:46,540
<i>I need you all to remain calm.</i>

84
00:04:46,832 --> 00:04:49,210
<i>These attackers are just thugs,</i>

85
00:04:49,376 --> 00:04:51,712
<i>brought on by the lowest element.</i>

86
00:04:52,046 --> 00:04:53,214
I'm not gonna take this...

87
00:04:53,255 --> 00:04:55,800
<i>The Duchess Satine
has led us to ruin!</i>

88
00:04:58,385 --> 00:04:59,386
<i>Death Watch!</i>

89
00:05:00,054 --> 00:05:01,555
<i>Guards, stay back!</i>

90
00:05:02,056 --> 00:05:05,893
<i>Vizsla, you must be the one
responsible for these attacks!</i>

91
00:05:06,143 --> 00:05:07,978
<i>No, I am not responsible!</i>

92
00:05:08,229 --> 00:05:10,481
<i>But I can offer a solution.</i>

93
00:05:13,567 --> 00:05:15,236
<i>People of Mandalore!</i>

94
00:05:17,738 --> 00:05:20,574
<i>I am Pre Vizsla of Clan Vizsla.</i>

95
00:05:20,950 --> 00:05:22,409
<i>Death Watch is here to save you</i>

96
00:05:22,493 --> 00:05:26,163
<i>from these intergalactic gangsters
that threaten our great city.</i>

97
00:05:26,413 --> 00:05:27,414
<i>This is a war.</i>

98
00:05:28,082 --> 00:05:29,500
<i>And we will win.</i>

99
00:05:35,840 --> 00:05:39,969
<i>Join me and let us defend Mandalore
against the criminals.</i>

100
00:05:40,344 --> 00:05:43,180
<i>We need action, not pacifism.</i>

101
00:05:43,264 --> 00:05:45,099
<i>Do not listen to him!</i>

102
00:05:45,349 --> 00:05:49,144
<i>His war will cause the end of Mandalore
as we know it!</i>

103
00:05:49,436 --> 00:05:51,313
<i>We are under attack!</i>

104
00:05:51,438 --> 00:05:53,691
<i>There is no time for discussion!</i>

105
00:05:59,864 --> 00:06:04,702
<i>The name "Mandalore" should set fear
into the hearts of these gangsters.</i>

106
00:06:26,181 --> 00:06:32,021
<i>If the people are beginning to follow you,
it is time for Death Watch to take action.</i>

107
00:06:32,479 --> 00:06:34,398
<i>Make sure you put on a good show.</i>

108
00:06:35,232 --> 00:06:37,318
As you wish, Lord Maul.

109
00:06:53,334 --> 00:06:54,335
What should we do?

110
00:06:54,668 --> 00:06:56,045
There's nothing we can do.

111
00:06:56,253 --> 00:06:58,589
The Duchess's forces are being overrun

112
00:06:58,672 --> 00:07:00,758
across the entire planet.

113
00:07:00,841 --> 00:07:04,678
Listen. It sounds like
there is fighting going on out there.

114
00:07:08,933 --> 00:07:10,017
What's going on?

115
00:07:10,392 --> 00:07:13,020
We're Death Watch,
and we're here to rescue you.

116
00:07:13,187 --> 00:07:14,730
You have my thanks, soldier.

117
00:07:15,272 --> 00:07:17,524
No, thank Pre Vizsla.

118
00:07:54,186 --> 00:07:55,479
You're safe now.

119
00:07:57,982 --> 00:08:00,192
- It's Death Watch !
- Death Watch are our saviors!

120
00:08:00,275 --> 00:08:02,444
- They freed us.
- You're saviors!

121
00:08:02,528 --> 00:08:03,862
- We owe them our lives!
- They saved us!

122
00:08:07,366 --> 00:08:09,201
Stop them ! They've robbed the main vault!

123
00:08:19,545 --> 00:08:21,005
Keep up, you weaklings!

124
00:08:41,692 --> 00:08:45,320
This monster will not trouble
the people of Mandalore any longer.

125
00:08:45,904 --> 00:08:47,906
Take him away, Captain!

126
00:08:51,076 --> 00:08:55,372
Vizsla! Vizsla! Vizsla! Vizsla!

127
00:08:59,043 --> 00:09:02,087
Duchess, Pre Vizsla and his men
have entered the palace.

128
00:09:02,796 --> 00:09:04,715
-Should we stop them?
-How can we?

129
00:09:05,132 --> 00:09:07,259
The people are on their side now.

130
00:09:14,016 --> 00:09:16,935
No! There will be no bloodshed.

131
00:09:17,436 --> 00:09:18,520
But, Duchess!

132
00:09:18,645 --> 00:09:22,191
I will not be provoked to violence
by these terrorists.

133
00:09:22,357 --> 00:09:25,444
Listen, Duchess. Do you hear the people?

134
00:09:25,527 --> 00:09:27,905
They cry out for change.

135
00:09:28,197 --> 00:09:31,700
Your weak-minded rule of Mandalore
is at an end.

136
00:09:31,784 --> 00:09:34,411
The resurrection of our warrior past

137
00:09:34,495 --> 00:09:36,997
is about to begin.

138
00:09:44,671 --> 00:09:47,216
<i>Duchess Satine
and the New Mandalorian leaders</i>

139
00:09:47,299 --> 00:09:49,301
<i>have fled in cowardice</i>

140
00:09:49,384 --> 00:09:52,679
<i>while the Death Watch
brought these criminals to justice.</i>

141
00:09:53,263 --> 00:09:57,434
<i>Your new prime minister, Pre Vizsla,
leader of Death Watch,</i>

142
00:09:57,643 --> 00:09:59,603
<i>exiled governor of Concordia,</i>

143
00:09:59,686 --> 00:10:01,772
<i>true son of Mandalore,</i>

144
00:10:01,855 --> 00:10:06,360
<i>presents you with the lords of the
most feared crime families in the galaxy.</i>

145
00:10:06,527 --> 00:10:08,403
Vizsla! Vizsla! Vizsla!

146
00:10:20,165 --> 00:10:24,461
You cannot hold me here!
I am the Duchess of Mandalore!

147
00:10:24,962 --> 00:10:27,965
Your actions will bring
our civilization to ruin!

148
00:10:28,048 --> 00:10:30,717
-Is that you, Satine?
-Almec?

149
00:10:31,176 --> 00:10:35,264
Here for a visit?
Or has peace betrayed you, too, Duchess?

150
00:10:35,597 --> 00:10:38,475
Peace exists
only in the minds of the faithful.

151
00:10:38,684 --> 00:10:42,312
And faith has been
the greatest disappointment.

152
00:10:42,646 --> 00:10:44,565
Only when it is broken.

153
00:10:44,773 --> 00:10:47,442
What you did for the people
as prime minister

154
00:10:47,526 --> 00:10:48,986
betrayed their trust.

155
00:10:49,444 --> 00:10:53,574
And you betrayed mine.
Destitution leaves little room for faith.

156
00:10:53,699 --> 00:10:56,869
My actions allowed the people
hope in your leadership.

157
00:10:57,244 --> 00:11:00,789
The supplies I bought on the black market
kept you in power.

158
00:11:01,206 --> 00:11:03,417
Another error of judgment.

159
00:11:03,876 --> 00:11:07,379
The people made willing sacrifices
for their freedom.

160
00:11:07,421 --> 00:11:09,423
Corruption is not the answer.

161
00:11:11,592 --> 00:11:13,677
Then enjoy your freedom, Duchess.

162
00:11:13,886 --> 00:11:16,930
You'll have plenty of time
to tell me all about it.

163
00:11:26,064 --> 00:11:28,400
The transition of power will be seamless.

164
00:11:28,775 --> 00:11:32,112
We now have the support of the people,
and Satine to bait Kenobi.

165
00:11:32,738 --> 00:11:35,699
With his demise, our deal will be complete.

166
00:11:35,782 --> 00:11:38,202
Your oversight requires correction.

167
00:11:38,368 --> 00:11:41,121
We now have a base, an army,

168
00:11:41,413 --> 00:11:45,083
and the means to expand
to other neutral systems.

169
00:11:45,292 --> 00:11:48,295
It wasn't an oversight, it was intentional.

170
00:11:48,921 --> 00:11:51,298
I don't have an interest
in the other systems.

171
00:11:51,798 --> 00:11:53,592
Your vision no longer matters.

172
00:12:00,933 --> 00:12:03,477
Oh, don't fret! I'll still honor our deal.

173
00:12:03,644 --> 00:12:05,312
Kenobi will be dealt with.

174
00:12:05,896 --> 00:12:08,148
But now, you'll do as I say.

175
00:12:12,236 --> 00:12:14,071
<i>The violence is over!</i>

176
00:12:14,238 --> 00:12:18,283
<i>The last of the parasites infecting
Mandalore has been caught.</i>

177
00:12:18,992 --> 00:12:22,829
<i>The Duchess has abandoned her duty
to protect Mandalore.</i>

178
00:12:22,955 --> 00:12:26,917
<i>Her political dream only encourages
aggression against our planet.</i>

179
00:12:28,502 --> 00:12:33,507
<i>We have learned from this beast
the consequences of pacifist principles.</i>

180
00:12:33,632 --> 00:12:37,678
<i>It's now time to restore
the traditions of Mandalore!</i>

181
00:12:38,262 --> 00:12:41,181
<i>No one will ever threaten us again!</i>

182
00:12:41,473 --> 00:12:46,812
Vizsla! Vizsla! Vizsla! Vizsla! Vizsla!

183
00:12:54,528 --> 00:12:57,489
Vizsla has captured
the support of his people,

184
00:12:57,531 --> 00:12:59,157
just as we planned.

185
00:12:59,324 --> 00:13:02,661
However, he is not
their anointed leader yet.

186
00:13:02,744 --> 00:13:08,041
There is still time for us to put in place
a leader under our control.

187
00:13:09,209 --> 00:13:11,211
Then let us escape, and we shall find one!

188
00:13:11,753 --> 00:13:14,715
Patience. We must move cautiously.

189
00:13:14,840 --> 00:13:16,550
By placing us in prison,

190
00:13:16,591 --> 00:13:22,222
Vizsla has unwittingly put us in reach
of several candidates for his successor.

191
00:13:22,597 --> 00:13:23,890
Who do you mean, brother?

192
00:13:25,392 --> 00:13:28,729
Vizsla has imprisoned the Duchess here.

193
00:13:28,895 --> 00:13:32,691
Other political advisors of hers
will be within these walls

194
00:13:32,733 --> 00:13:35,736
whom will suit our purposes well.

195
00:13:35,861 --> 00:13:37,904
Hey, quiet, you two!

196
00:13:38,613 --> 00:13:42,200
Apprentice, I wish a tour of this facility.

197
00:14:08,143 --> 00:14:12,105
You are the now former
Duchess Satine, are you not?

198
00:14:13,398 --> 00:14:15,484
What do you want, you monster?

199
00:14:16,777 --> 00:14:19,613
Mmm. Nothing yet,
but I will have a use for you in time.

200
00:14:19,738 --> 00:14:22,491
Where are the other leaders
of your people?

201
00:14:22,616 --> 00:14:24,659
You should know already.

202
00:14:24,785 --> 00:14:28,288
They've either sided with Vizsla
or have been killed.

203
00:14:28,622 --> 00:14:31,333
There's no one left now but Almec and I,

204
00:14:31,458 --> 00:14:34,127
but he's as corrupt and vile as you.

205
00:14:34,419 --> 00:14:35,462
Really?

206
00:14:36,630 --> 00:14:38,965
Thank you for being so cooperative.

207
00:14:47,974 --> 00:14:49,101
Almec?

208
00:14:49,976 --> 00:14:50,977
Yes?

209
00:14:51,269 --> 00:14:53,355
I can deliver you from this prison.

210
00:14:53,980 --> 00:14:56,108
What was your position
in this government?

211
00:14:56,650 --> 00:14:58,485
I'm the former prime minister.

212
00:14:59,486 --> 00:15:02,489
Satine imprisoned me
on charges of corruption and conspiracy

213
00:15:02,531 --> 00:15:04,324
for using the black market.

214
00:15:05,826 --> 00:15:07,202
He's a murderer.

215
00:15:07,327 --> 00:15:10,580
-He calls the death of children...
-Quiet.

216
00:15:18,713 --> 00:15:19,840
What do you want from me?

217
00:15:20,257 --> 00:15:24,010
Mandalore is in need of a prime minister.

218
00:15:24,177 --> 00:15:26,680
I thought you were in league
with Pre Vizsla.

219
00:15:31,560 --> 00:15:32,727
We were.

220
00:15:33,520 --> 00:15:35,021
Oh, clearly, you are powerful.

221
00:15:35,188 --> 00:15:38,525
But how can two of you
overthrow Vizsla and his supporters?

222
00:15:39,109 --> 00:15:41,027
Vizsla is a soldier.

223
00:15:41,361 --> 00:15:44,906
And like every soldier,
he is bound by honor.

224
00:15:45,365 --> 00:15:48,285
I will challenge him
to single combat in front of his men.

225
00:15:48,535 --> 00:15:50,370
He will not deny me.

226
00:15:51,121 --> 00:15:53,248
Ooh, if you defeat him,

227
00:15:53,373 --> 00:15:55,876
according to the ancient laws of Mandalore

228
00:15:56,251 --> 00:15:59,379
his soldiers will be
honor-bound to follow you.

229
00:15:59,963 --> 00:16:01,214
Precisely.

230
00:16:04,718 --> 00:16:06,261
<i>Sir! They're attacking!</i>

231
00:16:19,816 --> 00:16:23,904
I challenge you, one warrior to another,

232
00:16:23,945 --> 00:16:27,824
and only the strongest
shall rule Mandalore.

233
00:16:33,121 --> 00:16:34,456
So be it.

234
00:16:34,581 --> 00:16:35,582
Give him his weapon.

235
00:16:45,133 --> 00:16:46,510
For Mandalore!

236
00:19:04,731 --> 00:19:06,107
Like you said,

237
00:19:06,816 --> 00:19:08,568
only the strongest

238
00:19:09,235 --> 00:19:10,570
shall rule.

239
00:19:20,830 --> 00:19:22,916
I claim this sword,

240
00:19:23,583 --> 00:19:28,463
and my rightful place
as leader of Death Watch.

241
00:19:32,300 --> 00:19:35,553
Never!
No outsider will ever rule Mandalore.

242
00:19:35,762 --> 00:19:36,888
Hmm.

243
00:19:36,930 --> 00:19:38,598
If you will not join me,

244
00:19:38,973 --> 00:19:41,142
you will all die.

245
00:19:43,436 --> 00:19:44,896
You're all traitors!

246
00:19:44,979 --> 00:19:49,567
Unfortunately for you,
history will not see it that way.

247
00:19:49,943 --> 00:19:51,111
Execute them!

248
00:20:21,307 --> 00:20:23,810
<i>Silence! Please! Silence!</i>

249
00:20:24,811 --> 00:20:26,312
<i>Hear me now!</i>

250
00:20:27,147 --> 00:20:31,901
<i>Duchess Satine, the so-called pacifist</i>

251
00:20:31,985 --> 00:20:35,405
<i>who could not protect you
when your lives were at stake,</i>

252
00:20:35,488 --> 00:20:37,907
<i>has murdered Pre Vizsla,</i>

253
00:20:37,991 --> 00:20:40,076
<i>The true hero of Mandalore.</i>

254
00:20:40,493 --> 00:20:42,996
<i>Satine is now under arrest,</i>

255
00:20:43,079 --> 00:20:45,915
<i>and it was Pre Vizsla's last command</i>

256
00:20:45,999 --> 00:20:49,419
<i>that I be reinstated as prime minister.</i>

257
00:20:49,794 --> 00:20:52,088
<i>I know my past is checkered,</i>

258
00:20:52,172 --> 00:20:56,176
<i>but I promise you,
I take full responsibility for my people.</i>

259
00:20:56,676 --> 00:21:00,472
<i>And my heart now bleeds for your pain.</i>

260
00:21:00,930 --> 00:21:06,102
<i>However, from this point on,
Mandalore will be strong,</i>

261
00:21:06,186 --> 00:21:11,858
<i>and we will be known as the warriors
we were always meant to be!</i>

262
00:21:25,622 --> 00:21:28,500
You have done well, Prime Minister.

263
00:21:28,875 --> 00:21:32,378
I shall waste no time
in building my administration.

264
00:21:32,712 --> 00:21:34,506
Choose wisely.

265
00:21:34,589 --> 00:21:38,176
I will hold you personally responsible
for their failures.

266
00:21:39,886 --> 00:21:40,929
Yes, master.

267
00:21:41,554 --> 00:21:44,724
Uh, is there anything more you require?

268
00:21:45,642 --> 00:21:46,726
Go.

269
00:21:47,435 --> 00:21:49,687
Rule my people.

270
00:21:49,711 --> 00:21:54,711
http://hiqve.com/

